dataset.description: Parcel Polygons. The dataset contains locations and attributes of Parcels, created as part of the Polk County Geographic Information System (Polk County GIS). The tax information (attribution) comes from Polk County Tax System Extract file. The creation of this layer is automated, occurs nightly, and uses the most currently available tax information.
dataset.title: Parcels
